{"type": "article", "id": 25737, "title": "CK男女装创意总监都将离职，以及，Chloé 夏日大片不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-04-20T10:41:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2532, "name": "袜子"}, {"id": 2528, "name": "离职"}, {"id": 18072, "name": "创意总监"}, {"id": 26481, "name": "MADE时装周"}, {"id": 3313, "name": "洛杉矶"}, {"id": 1130, "name": "手表"}, {"id": 6582, "name": "春夏"}, {"id": 142, "name": "视频"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 1612, "name": "Mac"}, {"id": 26482, "name": "Hearst"}, {"id": 16146, "name": "Complex"}, {"id": 2200, "name": "Moschino"}, {"id": 1066, "name": "Calvin Klein"}, {"id": 26424, "name": "巴黎欧莱雅"}, {"id": 2628, "name": "卡西欧"}, {"id": 976, "name": "Rihanna"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607135534QhHqfjn8UNTlzEp4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/francisco-costa-italo-zucchelli-calvin-klein-raf-simons-10414564/\"><b>Calvin Klein 男女装创意总监都将离职</b></a>｜Calvin Klein 及其母公司 PVH 集团昨日宣布，Calvin Klein 女装创意总监 Francisco Costa 和男装创意总监 Italo Zucchelli 将离职，两人皆在 2003 年联合创始人 Calvin Klein 和 Barry Schwartz 将公司卖给 PVH 集团并离开后开始任职。2016 秋季系列即他们在品牌的最后作品。这一变动也属于 Calvin Klein 并未完全透露的全球新战略一部分，还宣布品牌将不会参与六月的男装周以及九月的女装走秀，而是以 presentations 的形式取代。据传，去年十月卸任 Dior 创意总监的 Raf Simons 将成为 Calvin Klein 男女装创意总监。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/4/18/11453816/made-la-moschino-tyler-the-creator\"><b>Moschino 今年参加洛杉矶 Made 时装周</b></a>｜意大利奢侈品牌 Moschino 创意总监 Jeremy Scott ，今年六月将带品牌男装春夏系列、女装度假系列亮相 Made 时装周在洛杉矶的活动，后者作为纽约时装周官方日程中的一部分，以创意为核心，重在音乐、摄影等艺术元素的跨界，自 2009 年开始吸引众多新锐设计师品牌前来办展。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/beauty-features/loreal-paris-youtube-to-launch-beautytube-in-france-10414417/\"><b>欧莱雅为扶持美妆人才推出 YouTube 美妆频道</b></a>｜巴黎欧莱雅与 YouTube 合作，为选出法国美妆人才而推出 BeautyTUBE 美妆频道。预计在六月开始的首个版本将选出十位选手，他们的性别、年龄以及在 YouTube 上的粉丝将不会成为决定性因素。选出的六个月内将接受欧莱雅及 YouTube 高管的指导和训练，之后在 YouTube 上推出影片。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/hearst-verizon-complex-media-10413648/\"><b>Hearst 和 Verizon 联手收购 complex </b></a>｜传媒集团 Hearst 及美国电信运营商 Verizon 将联手收购 Complex Media，各自持有 50% 的股份，Complex Media 是潮流类型的生活方式网站，收购后仍将保持独立运营，联合创始人兼 CEO Rich Antoniello 也将继续领导公司。Complex Media 每月独立访问用户数超 5000 万，页面浏览量也达到了 3 亿次。据《华尔街日报》报道 ，Complex Media 的估值在 2.5 亿－ 3 亿美元之间。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/4/19/11462784/rihanna-stance-socks-spring-2016\">Rihanna 和袜子品牌 Stance 的第三波合作系列上市</a>，价格在 16－20 美元之间，Racked 形容像是绝代艳后 Marie Antoinette 穿去健身房的打扮。</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071355177Z4TxsoAYFB2nlL3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135517VvU2fgZLxQNEwHc3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135518N0sP5OGMjXLKepCZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135518pBQwmu3yejRr1ldW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.cn/fashion/other-stories-ready-for-romance/\">&amp; Other Stories 最新春季 lookbook</a>，主打裸色：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135519p1BSIgm4M3KoWJEn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071355199pGxouijgSHdlX2B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135520qXz0p8ROSUefEDdy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135521uK8R2LZqgDwxeIyP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135522YceyAvFjwgmEZbIK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135523O60X59hFvCtwEzNe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2016/4/stussy-casio-g-shock-dw-5600-2016\">潮流服饰品牌 Stussy 与卡西欧再次推出合作款  G-SHOCK</a>，黑白两色的 DW-5600 预计于 4 月 22 日上市：<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071355237AST6HEd9qWhInKp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135523kZm3zaqge7dfG8Cw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">Chloé 拍摄最新 2016 年 Sun 系列夏季广告，以夏日的公路旅行为灵感：<span style=\"text-align: center;\"> </span></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135524yXGASOfl2LmCaENz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135524u1padiU8E0TbOLvI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135525s6XUQfbFBkl3WM2I.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071355257NRKwosDeZMrOl59.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135526qMzLReEUZX0VgPaO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135526sNlOCWEJcI4b7g0e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135526ZP0fKiFt7VhdYIgp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135527LDqtV2ObvyTNliks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135527OcASLWapM2BsyGgY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3296875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/4/19/11459354/mac-good-luck-trolls-collection\">MAC 彩妆要推出巨魔娃娃（troll doll ）系列</a>，这个 1959 年诞生的五颜六色竖起头发的卡通形象对于 90 年代美国年轻人来说非常具有代表性。预计 7 月 28 日开始在线发售，8 月 4 日进驻门店。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071355281OPGkFzMh6if79Tm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135528hGlLwx7DdIng5ofa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.29375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">近几年几乎成为“爆款制造机”的 Gucci ，<a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/4/18/11441490/gucci-sneakers-ace#6429859\">2016 年早秋系列的球鞋新款  Ace sneaker</a>，怎么看都有点要成为“街鞋”的意思：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135529CHmhcQpx1qiSl9sw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135529tqwarUfj9Rl2165v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135530rtzMbCFIipTkNufH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/stripe-styles-j-crew-trend/\"> J. CREW 新一季推出了更多的条纹款</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135531On4tWoazwFqmb6Yv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.26\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135531aizwdF9jvhLeNtqZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.26\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135532BcqnRlOifN21IVYK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.26\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713553238rZKiUvsmdCgYf5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25891182\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071355333wiIYrk1nXo4GDMg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.26\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135533fB6lEt4bSVjWJmrR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.26\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n"}